# Dev Server Rules

If the servers aren't running and you need to start them, we run them with pnpm run dev from project root. This uses [start-servers.ts](mdc:scripts/start-servers.ts) to start them both, this will also start our docker containers if they're not running.

You don't need to restart the servers everytime you make a change because we have hot reload enabled on the servers.